text: What are the benefits of listing my car with AutoBrand?
answer: Listing your car with AutoBrand connects you to a vast community of eager buyers and enthusiasts looking for their next vehicle. Our platform provides cutting-edge marketing features, expert assistance, and analytics to help your listing shine and attract the right buyers swiftly

text: What is the Commission Fee?
answer: AutoBrand charges a 5% commission on the final sale price.Example: If a car sells for NGN 3,000,000, AutoBrand keeps NGN 150,000 and you receive NGN 2,850,000. This fee covers marketing, exposure, secure transactions, and support.

text: What is the Payment Process?
answer: All payments are made securely through the AutoBrand platform.Funds are held in escrow until the buyer confirms delivery.Payouts (after 5% commission) are processed within 3-5 business days to your registered bank account.

text: How do we dectect any unusal listing?
answer: AutoBrand may remove false or suspicious listings, request verification, and suspend users for fraud. Legal action may be taken.

text: How do I list my car?
answer: Listing your vehicle is easy! Simply sign in to your account and navigate to the "List a Car section". Fill out the required details, including vehicle type, location, price, and description. Upload high-quality photos, review your information, and click Submit. Once approved, your vehicle will be live on our platform

text: What is the typical duration of the car listing process?
answer: The car listing process usually takes around 24 to 48 hours. This timeframe can vary based on how complete your information is and if any extra verification steps are needed. Well keep you informed at every stage to guarantee a seamless and prompt listing experience.

text: Can I edit my Car Listing?
answer: Yes, you can edit your vehicle listing at any time. But it is important to ensure that all details are correct before you submit. Just log into your account, go to your listings, and double-check everything. If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team!
